Description: # Yoku
        
        A minimal Yahoo! Auctions scraper deployed as a Telegram bot.
        
        ## Installation
        
        ```shell
        pip install yoku
        ```
        
        ## Deployment
        
        - Request a bot token from BotFather on Telegram.
        
        - Ensure that the `YOKU_BOT_TOKEN` environment variable is set.
        
        ```shell
        yoku
        ```
        
        ## Bot Usage
        
        Add a query
        
        ```
        /add <query>
        ```
        
        Remove a query
        
        ```
        /rm <query>
        ```
        
        List queries
        
        ```
        /ls
        ```
        
        Fetch queries
        
        ```
        /force
        ```
        
